This will check that merged branches are VERIFIED FIXED and unmerged
branches are not.

Usage: ./check-release-hygiene <tag of previous release> <bugzilla username>

You will need to edit the script if new modules have been added to the release.

You may need:

# apt-get install libsoap-lite-perl libterm-readpassword-perl

If it breaks you get to keep both pieces.

On Mac-Os you can use cpan to get missing Perl packages
for example:
  sudo cpan install Term::ReadPassword
